The paper discusses the downlink spectral efficiency of a cell-free Massive MIMO system with full pilot zero forcing precoding, which involves techniques related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), signal processing (cs.SI), communication (cs.COMM), and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
